                "invention-title": "Combination unit for hydrogen manufacture by electric energy and hydrogen electricity generation"
            },
            "abstract": {
                "p": "The invention relates to a combination device for electric-energy hydrogen production and hydrogen-energy power generation, and belongs to the two technical fields which are the electrolysis as well as hydrogen and the power energy conversion. For achieving power-hydrogen-power energy conversion process, a DC power 1, an electrolyzed water hydrogen making device 2 and a hydrogen fuel battery 3 are used integrally, which is characterized in that: the DC power 1 is connected with the electrolyzed water hydrogen making device 2; the DC power 1 can electrolyze the water in the electrolyzed water hydrogen making device 2 to obtain hydrogen; the hydrogen in the electrolyzed water hydrogen making device 2 is transferred into the hydrogen fuel battery 3 and can be conversed into the power energy. The invention has the advantages that the substance structure of the water can be changed through power energy to the substance manner of hydrogen and oxygen to release the chemical energy stored in the water substance structure, and then the chemical energy can be re-conversed into the convenient power energy which is roughly equal to the original power energy plus the chemical energy."
